  <entry xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en">
    <id>http://versewisconsin.org/Issue110/audio.html</id>
    <title>At Wounded Knee</title>
    <subtitle>Poem text in Verse Wisconsin #110 print; link is to audio only</subtitle>
    <updated>2012-01-02</updated>
    <link href="http://versewisconsin.org/Issue110/audio.html"/>
    <source>
      <id>http://versewisconsin.org</id>
      <title>Verse Wisconsin</title>
    </source>
    <author>
      <name>Uche Ogbuji</name>
      <uri>http://uche.ogbuji.net</uri>
      <email>uche@ogbuji.net</email>
    </author>
    <summary type="xhtml">
      <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
        <pre>The bumblebee at wounded knee
Decants his nectar lazily
Yellow lines dance into black
And when we dream we hear the crack
And when we dream we see the flash
We shake from cold, we smell the ash
        </pre>
      </div>
    </summary>
  </entry>

